  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔻Arksync is a fast-paced sci-fi action game where a small robot teddy bear hijacks a powerful assault android and sets out across the Trash Moon in search of their lost owner.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge weapons, fight hostile machines, and uncover the secrets buried beneath a world built from humanity's discarded technology.<br><br>Every step across the Trash Moon brings the toy bear closer to finding their friend. <br><br><strong>🔻Key Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore <strong>12 Levels</strong> within the Trash moon and beyond</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight <strong>8+ Enemy Types</strong> including drones, mechs, and zombies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive <strong>11 Boss Fights</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield <strong>9 Weapons, and 6 Utilities</strong> with unique tactical combinations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Discover hidden <strong>Mini-games</strong> and unexpected gameplay twists</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/1d6b15c3d77512b92b3b96e25985ec92.poster.avif?t=1773185152\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/1d6b15c3d77512b92b3b96e25985ec92.webm?t=1773185152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/1d6b15c3d77512b92b3b96e25985ec92.mp4?t=1773185152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔻Explore the Trash Moon</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Trash Moon<strong> </strong>has become a massive dumping ground for abandoned machines and failed corporate experiments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore dangerous facilities, ruined infrastructure, and strange anomalies scattered across the moon as you search for <strong>Encryption Disks (E-Disks)</strong> needed to unlock deeper sectors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repair broken systems like excavation elevators, tram stations, and ancient machinery to open new levels throughout the world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/df87fea9c390af181e5819f903c06e48.poster.avif?t=1773185152\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/df87fea9c390af181e5819f903c06e48.webm?t=1773185152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/df87fea9c390af181e5819f903c06e48.mp4?t=1773185152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔻Combat with an Arsenal of Weapons and Utilities</strong><br>Face corrupted drones, rogue machines, and strange infected entities lurking within the scrap.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master a wide variety of weapons and utilities. Loadouts encourage different play styles, and strategies.<br><br><strong>🔻Fast Movement and Reactive Combat</strong><br>You were built for confrontation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use <strong>jump thrusters, dodge boosts, and rapid movement</strong> to survive ambushes and navigate dangerous environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay mobile, adapt quickly, and turn the battlefield in your favor.<br><br><strong>🔻Persistent Death System</strong> <br>    Your android body is linked to a <strong>Reboot Terminal</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If destroyed, you are rebuilt — but everything you carried is lost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every expedition becomes a calculated risk.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/287df783e0fb03354cb5101039edd78b.poster.avif?t=1773185152\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/287df783e0fb03354cb5101039edd78b.webm?t=1773185152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/287df783e0fb03354cb5101039edd78b.mp4?t=1773185152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔻Customize Your Loadout</strong><br>    Weapons can be modified with unique <strong>Mod Schematics</strong>, allowing players to experiment with powerful combinations.<br>Visit <strong>Dispensers</strong> and <strong>Depots</strong> to resupply ammunition, shields, and new equipment before heading back into the scrap. <br>Preparation is the difference between survival and destruction. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/448c68ec50c85ce52a678716cd6ecced.poster.avif?t=1773185152\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/448c68ec50c85ce52a678716cd6ecced.webm?t=1773185152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/448c68ec50c85ce52a678716cd6ecced.mp4?t=1773185152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔻Recover the Encryption Disks</strong><br>    Deep within the Trash Moon lie the <strong>E-Disks</strong> required to unlock restricted areas and uncover the secrets of the Trash Moon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each discovery brings you closer to <strong>returning the robot teddy bear to the human they call friend.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/bfcc1fe6da6df144d8a5e850ef658237.poster.avif?t=1773185152\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/bfcc1fe6da6df144d8a5e850ef658237.webm?t=1773185152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/bfcc1fe6da6df144d8a5e850ef658237.mp4?t=1773185152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/f8dcf17f0d774f43a74c148d0a77e17a.poster.avif?t=1773185152\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/f8dcf17f0d774f43a74c148d0a77e17a.webm?t=1773185152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828800/extras/f8dcf17f0d774f43a74c148d0a77e17a.mp4?t=1773185152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
